      • Time

        public Time(java.lang.String date,

            java.lang.String category,
            java.lang.String note,
            int calendarID,
            int timeID)
        Constructor
        Parameters:
        date - is the date to which this time object is assigned to
        startTime - is the start time as local time object
        endTime - is the end time as local time object
        totalTime - is the total time as double
        category - is the name of the category as String
        note - is the note to this time as a String
        calendarID - is the id of the date in the database as integer
        timeID - is the id of the time in the database as integer
